headline: KEY PRIVATE BANK HONORED FOR 'PRIVATE BANKING CLIENT SERVICE' AT THE 2025 PRIVATE ASSET MANAGEMENT AWARDS
summary: Key Private Bank, the wealth management division of KeyCorp (NYSE:KEY), was awarded for the best "Private Banking Client Service" at the Private Asset Management (PAM) Awards in New York City.
